'''塞斯·阿伯拉姆森'''（Seth Abramson，{{bd|1976年|10月31日}}），出生於[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[康科德_(马萨诸塞州)|康科德]]，是一名美国诗人兼律师。

==生活==
阿伯拉姆森是[[达特茅斯学院|达特茅斯学院]]、[[哈佛大学法学院|哈佛大学法学院]]和[[艾奥瓦大学|艾奥瓦大学]]的{{link-en|艾奥瓦作家工作室|Iowa Writers' Workshop}}的毕业生。他目前是[[威斯康辛大学麦迪逊分校|威斯康辛大学麦迪逊分校]]的英语博士研究生。<ref>Author biography, ''{{link-en|AGNI (杂志)|AGNI (magazine)|AGNI}}''. http://www.bu.edu/agni/authors/S/Seth-Abramson.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.bu.edu/agni/authors/S/Seth-Abramson.html |date=20091212080841 }}]</ref>

他已在《{{link-en|AGNI (杂志)|AGNI (magazine)|AGNI}}》、《{{link-en|The Alaska Quarterly Review|The Alaska Quarterly Review}}》、《{{link-en|The American Poetry Review|The American Poetry Review}}》、《{{link-en|Barn Owl Review|Barn Owl Review}}》、《{{link-en|Boston Review|Boston Review}}》、<ref>"The Ark Of," ''{{link-en|Boston Review|Boston Review}}''. http://bostonreview.net/BR31.4/abramson.html {{Wayback|url=http://bostonreview.net/BR31.4/abramson.html |date=20080516034419 }}</ref>出版《{{link-en|Colorado Review|Colorado Review}}》、《{{link-en|Concho River Review|Concho River Review}}》、《{{link-en|Conjunctions|Conjunctions}}》、《{{link-en|Crazyhorse (杂志)|Crazyhorse (magazine)|Crazyhorse}}》、《{{link-en|Denver Quarterly|Denver Quarterly}}》、《{{link-en|The Florida Review|The Florida Review}}》、《{{link-en|The Gettysburg Review|The Gettysburg Review}}》、<ref>"Enki and Inanna, After the Underworld," ''{{link-en|The Gettysburg Review|The Gettysburg Review}}''. http://www.gettysburgreview.com/selections/past_selections/index.dot?inode=2584552&pageTitle=Enki%20and%20Inanna,%20after%20the%20Underworld&crumbTitle=Enki%20and%20Inanna,%20after%20the%20Underworld&author=Seth%20Abramson&story=true {{Wayback|url=http://www.gettysburgreview.com/selections/past_selections/index.dot?inode=2584552&pageTitle=Enki%20and%20Inanna,%20after%20the%20Underworld&crumbTitle=Enki%20and%20Inanna,%20after%20the%20Underworld&author=Seth%20Abramson&story=true |date=20110711091136 }}</ref>《{{link-en|Green Mountains Review|Green Mountains Review}}》、《{{link-en|Harvard Review|Harvard Review}}》、《{{link-en|Indiana Review|Indiana Review}}》、《{{link-en|The Iowa Review|The Iowa Review}}》、《{{link-en|jubilat|jubilat}}》、《{{link-en|New American Writing|New American Writing}}》、《{{link-en|New York Quarterly|New York Quarterly}}》、《{{link-en|Pleiades (杂志)|Pleiades (journal)|Pleiades}}》、《{{link-en|Poetry (杂志)|Poetry (magazine)|Poetry}}》、《Poetry Daily》、<ref>"On Apollinaire's 'Lundi rue Christine,'" ''Poetry Daily''. {{cite web |url=http://poems.com/Poets%20Picks/Seth_Abramson.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090929050423/http://poems.com/Poets%20Picks/Seth_Abramson.html |archivedate=2009-09-29 }}</ref>《{{link-en|Potomac Review|Potomac Review}}》、《{{link-en|Salmagundi (杂志)|Salmagundi (magazine)|Salmagundi}}》、《{{link-en|The Southern Review|The Southern Review}}》、<ref>"Valentine to a Blackguard," ''{{link-en|The Southern Review|The Southern Review}}''.  http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_hb3549/is_/ai_n29265098?tag=untagged</ref>《{{link-en|Subtropics (杂志)|Subtropics (journal)|Subtropics}}》、《{{link-en|Sycamore Review|Sycamore Review}}》、<ref>"Gainsborough Paints Man Into Rocks," ''{{link-en|Sycamore Review|Sycamore Review}}''. http://www.sycamorereview.com/2006/01/gainsborough-paints-man-into-rocks/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.sycamorereview.com/2006/01/gainsborough-paints-man-into-rocks/ |date=20111009030805 }}</ref>《{{link-en|Third Coast (杂志)|Third Coast (magazine)|Third Coast}}》、《Verse Daily》、<ref>"Say the Boy," ''Verse Daily''. http://www.versedaily.org/2006/saytheboy.shtml {{Wayback|url=http://www.versedaily.org/2006/saytheboy.shtml |date=20180805155152 }}</ref><ref>"Lullaby," ''Verse Daily''. http://www.versedaily.org/2007/lullaby.shtml {{Wayback|url=http://www.versedaily.org/2007/lullaby.shtml |date=20190902174751 }}</ref>等出版物上发表过诗。

阿伯拉姆森创办了《''The Suburban Ecstasies''》，這是一个对美国艺术硕士专业（MFA Programs）进行排名的网站，排名是通过在当前的申请人中进行民意调查来确定的。<ref>"A Setting for Grad Writers", ''{{link-en|UCSD Guardian|UCSD Guardian}}'', Joanna Cardenas, March 30, 2009. {{cite web |url=http://www.ucsdguardian.org/focus/a-setting-for-grad-writers-1.1634596 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090403005158/http://www.ucsdguardian.org/focus/a-setting-for-grad-writers-1.1634596 |archivedate=2009-04-03 }}</ref>2009年10月，《''{{link-en|Poets & Writers|Poets & Writers}}''》发布了这些排名，这个排名是史上第一次对美国国内的写作艺术硕士专业进行的综合排名。<ref>"2010 MFA Rankings: The Top 50," ''{{link-en|Poets & Writers|Poets & Writers}}''. https://www.pw.org/content/2010_mfa_rankings_top_fifty_0 {{Wayback|url=https://www.pw.org/content/2010_mfa_rankings_top_fifty_0 |date=20210126182438 }}</ref><ref>"The Top 50 MFA Programs," ''{{link-en|Poets & Writers|Poets & Writers}}''. https://www.pw.org/content/top_fifty_mfa_programs_united_states_comprehensive_guide {{Wayback|url=https://www.pw.org/content/top_fifty_mfa_programs_united_states_comprehensive_guide |date=20210126124650 }}</ref>2009年11月9日，他不再继续撰写博客。

阿伯拉姆森曾是公设辩护律师、杂志编辑和{{link-en|Air America (广播)|Air America (radio network)|Air America}}广播评论员，於2005年获得了Koufax奖提名。<ref>[http://media.www.hlrecord.org/media/storage/paper609/news/2005/09/22/News/Living.On.Lipp-996018.shtml?norewrite200611151509&sourcedomain=www.hlrecord.org&&&xmlsyn=1 "Living on LIPP," ''{{link-en|Harvard Law Record|Harvard Law Record}}'' (September 22, 2005)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927021313/http://media.www.hlrecord.org/media/storage/paper609/news/2005/09/22/News/Living.On.Lipp-996018.shtml?norewrite200611151509&sourcedomain=www.hlrecord.org&&&xmlsyn=1 |date=2007年9月27日 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.nashuatelegraph.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20060730/ENTERTAINMENT/107300117 "Poets Have Statewide Outlet Thanks to New Hampshire Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nashuatelegraph.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20060730%2FENTERTAINMENT%2F107300117 |date=20090126101413 }}," ''{{link-en|The Telegraph (Nashua)|The Nashua Telegraph}}'' (July 30, 2006)</ref>

